# SkillSync â€“ AI Skill Matching & Career Recommendation System

This project started as an idea: *What if resume screening and job matching could be automated using AI agents working together?*  
SkillSync is my attempt to explore how multi-agent LLM systems can help match people with the right roles and suggest how they can improve their skills.

---

## ğŸ“Œ About the Project
Recruiters spend a lot of time manually reviewing resumes and comparing them with job descriptions.  
With SkillSync, I built a small AI workflow that simulates an intelligent hiring assistant.

The system can:
- Read and understand a candidateâ€™s skills
- Analyze job requirements
- Compare both and estimate job fit
- Suggest missing skills and career improvements

This project helped me learn how **multi-agent AI systems** can automate real HR workflows.

